description:
Robert en Bertrand is a Flemish comic series set during the 19th century in Belgium and France. It was created by Willy Vandersteen who also created famous Flemish series as Suske en Wiske, Jerom, De Rode Ridder and many others. The original language is Dutch. Unfortunately the series had an untimely end in 1993 just two issues short of it's 100 issue.

The series is about two vagrants that are being chased by a detective - called 'Number 17', who's trying to get them arrested for vagrancy.
name: Robert en Bertrand
